VALUES
  ('dietitian-moex-09674', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在尿中如果有葡萄糖，這些葡萄糖不會是：', '["從腎絲球濾過的", "從腎小管再吸收後剩下的", "從腎小管分泌的", "原來是在血漿中的"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2165ea180c34", "answer_pdf_sha1": "43829f5695ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09675', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個健康男子，平時飯前血糖100 mg/dL，並無糖尿病，此人之腎臟對葡萄糖的廓清率（clearance）是：', '["6000 mg/h", "100 mg/dL", "0 L/h", "無法評估"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2165ea180c34", "answer_pdf_sha1": "43829f5695ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09676', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於腎小管對鈉的處理，下列何者正確？', '["醛固酮（aldosterone）是調控近曲小管（proximal tubules）再吸收鈉的主要生理賀爾蒙", "在亨利氏迴（Henle’s loop）上升支（ascending limb）的上部（upper portion），鈉的再吸收伴隨著水分", "外傷失血，血壓降低時，醛固酮分泌減少", "腎小管任何一段對鈉的再吸收，主要經由主動運輸"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2165ea180c34", "answer_pdf_sha1": "43829f5695ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09677', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '在血鉀過高的病人，最可能觀察到或發生：', '["近曲小管（proximal tubules）對鉀的再吸收減弱", "醛固酮（aldosterone）分泌減弱", "血中副甲狀腺（parathyroid gland）賀爾蒙增加", "皮質集尿管（cortical collecting ducts）對鈉的再吸收增強"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2165ea180c34", "answer_pdf_sha1": "43829f5695ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-09678', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-096-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '某人有甲狀腺功能低下症狀，下列敘述何者正確？', '["若是因為飲食碘攝取量不足，給予放射性碘治療會改善", "若給予甲狀腺刺激素（TSH）測試，甲狀腺素釋放量可以提升，這病人甲狀腺必是肥大", "若發生在出生後至兒童期，此病人將會有呆小症（cretinism）", "若發生在成年期，會有心跳變快、血壓增高、甚至左心室肥厚，及心臟衰竭"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2165ea180c34", "answer_pdf_sha1": "43829f5695ef", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "096040", "c": "112", "s": "1001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "096", "exam_name": "096年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫、心理、呼吸治療、營養師、獸醫人員考試暨醫師分試考試第一試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
